    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Embark on a Treacherous Pilgrimage</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guide <strong>Mae</strong> on a coming-of-age pilgrimage in this heartfelt precision platformer, designed for both newcomers and those in search of a challenge.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273110/extras/8a291a1d76dc0b134d53bb8cd2b09fa8.poster.avif?t=1768958876\" width=780 height=305 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273110/extras/8a291a1d76dc0b134d53bb8cd2b09fa8.webm?t=1768958876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>For hundreds of years, the Mountain Shaman have used their powers of <strong>Astral Projection</strong> to travel vast distances. But Mae is different – her spirit travel is limited by a tether. When the time comes for a coming of age pilgrimage, Mae must forgo spirit flight and take the journey the long way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273110/extras/fc4a55ae1cb9ff9972aab27b7bcf5ba2.poster.avif?t=1768958876\" width=780 height=305 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273110/extras/fc4a55ae1cb9ff9972aab27b7bcf5ba2.webm?t=1768958876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br> <br>Join Mae on her challenging journey, using tough but satisfying platforming to leap and bound towards her goal. Master seven different Azae that change how your spirit interacts with the environment. Scour the world for secrets, treasures and hidden paths – your curiosity will be rewarded!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Precision and depth: </strong>Progressively unlock seven different spirit abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Seek and find: </strong>Discover hidden secrets, alternate paths and more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pure precision platforming: </strong>No combat, powerups or skill trees</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A speedrunner’s dream: </strong>Push your skills to the limit with timed runs!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tough but forgiving: </strong>Frequent checkpoints help you learn from your mistakes</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Full of heart: </strong>Discover a story about community, difference and growing up</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273110/extras/a2e9974b0ee864dc9f4b068dcd25898b.avif?t=1768958876\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273110/extras_big/a2e9974b0ee864dc9f4b068dcd25898b.avif?t=1768958876 width=800 height=119 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
